{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, applications focused on cerebral processes (e.g., attention span, decision-making, creativity) and their understanding can be developed (e.g., Yang et al. 2019; Zhang et al. 2019).",
    "It is recommended for their development that the interaction be Interactive or Explorative, depending on the task to be evaluated.",
    "For instance, an Explorative application may be useful to assess user point of focus and thereby to measure attention.",
    "In contrast, it seems more reasonable to propose a specific task to the users for the rest of the processes, to assess their performance without letting them move around the scenario.",
    "EEG sensors are essential as the objective is to observe and to understand brain processes."
  ]
}